          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "By seeing the reviews I can confirm you that 3/4th of the 5 stars reviews are posted by the school teachers and staffs, from this itself u can tell how manipulating the school is, studying in this school depends on entirely on your luck, you may get a airy class or exact opposite of a class with just 1window with no air circulation and tight area, water is not available in restrooms which is a nightmare.Teaching is full of a rush till the schooling end.U are allowed to enter the school only if u wear the low quality blue striped grey socks which is provided by the school at the cost of 240rs.There is nothing to talk about more..Disappointed",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
