          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My sister's daughter is studying here. She literally facing torchers every day. Teachers corner student who they don't like and treat them very badly. We raised a complaint to the management but they are not ready to hear.\nReally a worst management, teachers behaves very rude except few. Moreover teachers expects students to join tuitions running by them, otherwise they go extend to fail students to their subjects. This school is like a prison environment. My humble request please don't spoil your child future by joining this school (especially Ayyapakkam branch, I'm not sure about other branches though)\nKindly think twice before getting admission for your kids. Thank you.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
